<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Станьте организатором - Вакация</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bellota:wght@400;700&family=Manrope:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css?v=<%= Date.now() %>">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif; }
        h1, h2, h3 { font-family: 'Bellota', cursive; }
        
        .container-main {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        /* Benefits Section - Bento Grid Style */
        .benefits-creative {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(12, 1fr);
            grid-auto-rows: 300px;
            gap: 24px;
            margin: 80px 0;
        }
        .benefit-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 40px;
            padding: 40px;
            border: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
            transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: flex-end;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.02);
        }
        .benefit-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            border-color: var(--primary-purple);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(99, 91, 255, 0.1);
        }
        .benefit-card.large { grid-column: span 7; }
        .benefit-card.medium { grid-column: span 5; }
        .benefit-card.purple { background: var(--primary-purple); color: white; }
        .benefit-card.purple h3 { color: white !important; }
        .benefit-card.purple p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8) !important; }
        
        .benefit-icon-box {
            width: 64px;
            height: 64px;
            background: #f8f7ff;
            border-radius: 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: var(--primary-purple);
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .benefit-card.purple .benefit-icon-box {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            color: white;
        }
        .benefit-card:hover .benefit-icon-box {
            transform: scale(1.1) rotate(5deg);
        }
        .benefit-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif !important;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }
        .benefit-card p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: #64748b;
            margin: 0;
        }

        @media (max-width: 992px) {
            .benefits-creative { grid-template-columns: 1fr; grid-auto-rows: auto; }
            .benefit-card { grid-column: span 1 !important; min-height: 250px; }
        }

        .steps-section {
            margin: 120px 0;
            position: relative;
        }
        .steps-section h2 {
            font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif !important;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: -2px;
        }
        .steps-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            gap: 40px;
            position: relative;
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        /* Змейка (линия) */
        .steps-grid::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 40px;
            bottom: 40px;
            left: 50%;
            width: 2px;
            background: repeating-linear-gradient(180deg, var(--primary-purple) 0, var(--primary-purple) 10px, transparent 10px, transparent 20px);
            opacity: 0.15;
            z-index: 0;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
        }
        .step-item {
            background: #fff;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            z-index: 2;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            min-height: 180px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.02);
        }
        .step-item:hover {
            border-color: var(--primary-purple);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(99, 91, 255, 0.1);
        }
        /* Смещение для эффекта змейки */
        .step-item:nth-child(odd) {
            transform: translateY(-20px);
        }
        .step-item:nth-child(even) {
            transform: translateY(20px);
        }
        .step-item:nth-child(odd):hover {
            transform: translateY(-25px) scale(1.02);
        }
        .step-item:nth-child(even):hover {
            transform: translateY(15px) scale(1.02);
        }
        .step-number {
            font-size: 5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--primary-purple);
            opacity: 0.1;
            position: absolute;
            top: 10px;
            right: 30px;
            z-index: 1;
            line-height: 1;
        }
        .step-item h4 {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 3;
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 1.4rem;
        }
        .step-item p {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 3;
            color: #64748b;
            font-size: 15px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin: 0;
        }
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .steps-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .steps-grid::before { left: 20px; transform: none; }
            .step-item:nth-child(odd), .step-item:nth-child(even) { transform: none; }
        }

        /* Form & FAQ Grid */
        .form-faq-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 80px;
            margin-bottom: 100px;
            align-items: start;
            background: white;
            padding: 40px 80px;
            border-radius: 48px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(99, 91, 255, 0.1);
        }
        .application-form {
            background: transparent;
            padding: 0;
            border-radius: 0;
            box-shadow: none;
            border: none;
        }
        .application-form h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-top: 60px;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            line-height: 1;
            font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif !important;
            letter-spacing: -1.5px;
        }
        .form-group { margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .form-group label { 
            display: block; 
            font-weight: 700; 
            margin-bottom: 8px; 
            font-size: 14px;
            color: var(--text-dark);
        }
        .form-group input, .form-group textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 16px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            background: #f8fafc;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        .form-group input:focus, .form-group textarea:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: var(--primary-purple);
            background: white;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(99, 91, 255, 0.1);
        }
        .checkbox-group {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .checkbox-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 12px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #64748b;
            line-height: 1.4;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .checkbox-item input {
            margin-top: 3px;
            width: 18px;
            height: 18px;
            accent-color: var(--primary-purple);
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        .btn-submit {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 18px;
            border-radius: 18px;
            background: var(--primary-purple);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            font-weight: 800;
            font-size: 18px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(99, 91, 255, 0.2);
        }
        .btn-submit:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(99, 91, 255, 0.3);
            background: #4f46e5;
        }

        /* FAQ Style from Contacts Page */
        .faq-section h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            line-height: 1;
            font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif !important;
            letter-spacing: -1.5px;
        }
        .faq-item { margin-bottom: 24px; }
        .faq-item h4 { font-size: 17px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--text-dark); margin-top: 0; }
        .faq-item p { color: #64748b; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 15px; margin: 0; }

        /* Alt CTA */
        .alt-cta {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 100px;
        }
        .cta-box {
            padding: 60px;
            border-radius: 60px;
            min-height: 400px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        @media (max-width: 992px) {
            .benefit-row, .benefit-row:nth-child(even) { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; }
            .steps-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
            .form-faq-grid, .alt-cta { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('../partials/header') %>

    <main class="become-organizer-main">
        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <section class="hero-organizer" style="margin: 40px 20px 80px; min-height: 550px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; text-align: center; position: relative; overflow: hidden; background: var(--primary-purple); border-radius: 40px;">
            <div class="hero-decorations" style="position: absolute; width: 100%; height: 100%; top: 0; left: 0; pointer-events: none;">
                <div class="star-line" style="top: 15%; left: 10%; animation-delay: 0s;"></div>
                <div class="star-line" style="top: 40%; left: 60%; animation-delay: 2.5s;"></div>
                <div class="star-line" style="top: 20%; left: 85%; animation-delay: 5s;"></div>
                
                <div class="decor-item" style="top: 20%; left: 15%;">
                    <svg width="50" height="50" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" opacity="0.4"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <div class="decor-item" style="bottom: 25%; right: 15%; animation-delay: -3s;">
                    <svg width="60" height="60" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" opacity="0.3"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 8v8M8 12h8"/></svg>
                </div>
                
                <svg style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; opacity: 0.2;">
                    <path d="M 0 200 Q 300 100 600 200 T 1200 200" stroke="white" stroke-width="1" fill="none" class="line-anim" />
                    <path d="M 0 400 Q 300 450 600 400 T 1200 400" stroke="white" stroke-width="1" fill="none" class="line-anim" style="animation-delay: -7s;" />
                </svg>
            </div>

            <div class="container" style="position: relative; z-index: 10; max-width: 1000px; padding: 0 20px;">
                <div class="badge-hero" style="display: inline-block; background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2); color: #fff; padding: 10px 24px; border-radius: 100px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px; margin-bottom: 30px; border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);">
                    Для творцов и профессионалов
                </div>
                <h1 style="font-size: 5rem; font-weight: 800; color: #fff; margin: 0; line-height: 1.1; font-family: 'Bellota', cursive; letter-spacing: -2px;">
                    Станьте <span style="color: #fff; position: relative;">организатором<svg style="position: absolute; bottom: -5px; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 15px;" viewBox="0 0 100 15" preserveAspectRatio="none"><path d="M0,10 Q50,0 100,10" stroke="white" stroke-width="6" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></span>
                </h1>
                <p style="font-size: 24px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); margin-top: 35px; font-weight: 500; max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; line-height: 1.5;">
                    Проводите мероприятия, находите благодарную аудиторию<br>и не тратьте бюджет на слепую рекламу.
                </p>
                <div style="margin-top: 50px; display: flex; gap: 20px; justify-content: center;">
                    <a href="/auth/register" class="btn-hero-primary" style="background: #1e293b; color: #fff; padding: 20px 45px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 800; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.3s ease; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);">Начать бесплатно</a>
                    <a href="#benefits" class="btn-hero-secondary" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); color: #fff; padding: 20px 45px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 800; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.3s ease; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3); backdrop-filter: blur(10px);">Узнать больше</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <style>
            .star-line { position: absolute; width: 200px; height: 2px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.6), transparent); transform: rotate(-45deg); animation: starShoot 5s linear infinite; opacity: 0; }
            @keyframes starShoot { 0% { transform: translate(400px, -400px) rotate(-45deg); opacity: 0; } 10% { opacity: 0.8; } 30% { transform: translate(-800px, 800px) rotate(-45deg); opacity: 0; } 100% { transform: translate(-800px, 800px) rotate(-45deg); opacity: 0; } }
            .decor-item { position: absolute; animation: itemFloat 8s infinite ease-in-out; }
            @keyframes itemFloat { 0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0) rotate(0); } 50% { transform: translateY(-30px) rotate(10deg); } }
            .line-anim { stroke-dasharray: 1200; stroke-dashoffset: 1200; animation: lineFlow 20s linear infinite; }
            @keyframes lineFlow { to { stroke-dashoffset: 0; } }
            .btn-hero-primary:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3); background: #000; }
            .btn-hero-secondary:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.25); transform: translateY(-5px); }
            @media (max-width: 768px) { h1 { font-size: 3rem !important; } .btn-hero-primary, .btn-hero-secondary { padding: 15px 30px; font-size: 16px; } }
        </style>

        <div id="benefits" class="container-main">
            <div class="section-header" style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 80px; margin-top: 100px;">
                <h2 style="font-size: 4rem; font-weight: 800; margin: 0; font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif; letter-spacing: -2px; color: var(--text-dark);">Почему выбирают <span style="color: var(--primary-purple); position: relative; font-family: 'Bellota', cursive;">нас<svg style="position: absolute; bottom: -10px; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 12px;" viewBox="0 0 100 12" preserveAspectRatio="none"><path d="M0,10 Q50,0 100,10" stroke="var(--primary-purple)" stroke-width="4" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></span></h2>
                <p style="color: #64748b; font-size: 20px; margin-top: 20px; font-weight: 500;">Инструменты, которые работают на ваш успех</p>
            </div>

            <div class="benefits-creative">
                <div class="benefit-card large">
                    <div class="benefit-icon-box">
                        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 19V6M5 13l7-7 7 7"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Бесплатный анонс</h3>
                    <p>Размещайте мероприятия без абонентской платы<br>и скрытых платежей. Мы растем вместе с вами.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="benefit-card medium purple">
                    <div class="benefit-icon-box">
                        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="6"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Готовая аудитория</h3>
                    <p>Пользователи сами голосуют за идеи — вы сразу видите,<br>что востребовано.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="benefit-card medium">
                    <div class="benefit-icon-box">
                        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Модерация и поддержка</h3>
                    <p>Чистая лента без спама. Наша команда модераторов<br>помогает с оформлением каждого события.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="benefit-card large">
                    <div class="benefit-icon-box">
                        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="18" y1="20" x2="18" y2="10"/><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="4"/><line x1="6" y1="20" x2="6" y2="14"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Статистика и аналитика</h3>
                    <p>Полный контроль над процессом. Вы видите участников,<br>заполняемость мест и популярность в реальном времени.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <section class="steps-section">
                <div class="section-header" style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 60px;">
                    <h2 style="font-size: 3rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--text-dark);">Как стать организатором</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="steps-grid">
                    <div class="step-item">
                        <div class="step-number">1</div>
                        <h4 style="margin-top: 0;">Регистрация</h4>
                        <p>Зарегистрируйтесь или войдите в&nbsp;свой аккаунт на&nbsp;платформе.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="step-item">
                        <div class="step-number">2</div>
                        <h4 style="margin-top: 0;">Заявка</h4>
                        <p>Заполните простую форму ниже, чтобы мы&nbsp;узнали о&nbsp;вас больше.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="step-item">
                        <div class="step-number">3</div>
                        <h4 style="margin-top: 0;">Проверка</h4>
                        <p>Дождитесь подтверждения статуса (обычно это занимает 1–2&nbsp;дня).</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="step-item">
                        <div class="step-number">4</div>
                        <h4 style="margin-top: 0;">Старт</h4>
                        <p>Создавайте мероприятия&nbsp;и собирайте свою аудиторию!</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <div class="form-faq-grid">
                <section class="application-form">
                    <h2>Подать заявку</h2>
                    <form id="organizerRequestForm">
                        <input type="hidden" name="type" value="organizer_request">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label>Название организации / ИП / ФИО *</label>
                            <input type="text" name="org_name" placeholder="ИП Иванов И.И." required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label>Контактное лицо *</label>
                            <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Иван Иванов" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label>Email *</label>
                            <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="example@mail.com" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label>Телефон *</label>
                            <input type="tel" name="phone" placeholder="+7 (___) ___-__-__" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label>Ссылка на соцсети / сайт</label>
                            <input type="url" name="website" placeholder="https://vk.com/your_project">
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label>Краткое описание *</label>
                            <textarea name="message" rows="4" placeholder="Расскажите о вашем опыте..." required></textarea>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="checkbox-group">
                            <label class="checkbox-item">
                                <input type="checkbox" required>
                                <span>Я подтверждаю, что ознакомлен(а) с правилами для организаторов</span>
                            </label>
                            <label class="checkbox-item">
                                <input type="checkbox" required>
                                <span>Я даю согласие на обработку персональных данных</span>
                            </label>
                        </div>

                        <button type="submit" class="btn-submit">Отправить заявку</button>
                    </form>
                </section>

                <section class="faq-section">
                    <h2>FAQ</h2>
                    <div class="faq-list">
                        <div class="faq-item">
                            <h4>Сколько стоит размещение?</h4>
                            <p>Бесплатно. Комиссия берется только с продажи платных билетов (5–10%).</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq-item">
                            <h4>Как долго длится модерация?</h4>
                            <p>Обычно от 2 до 24 часов. Мы всегда присылаем уведомление о результате.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq-item">
                            <h4>Можно ли редактировать события?</h4>
                            <p>Да, но после внесения изменений мероприятие снова пройдет модерацию.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq-item">
                            <h4 style="margin-top: 0;">Как отслеживать участников?</h4>
                            <p>В личном кабинете организатора доступен полный список и статистика.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <a href="/help" class="all-faq-link" style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; color: var(--primary-purple); font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; margin-top: 30px; font-size: 16px; transition: all 0.3s ease;">
                        Все вопросы <span style="transition: transform 0.3s ease;">→</span>
                    </a>
                </section>
            </div>

            <style>
                .all-faq-link:hover span { transform: translateX(5px); }
                .all-faq-link:hover { color: #4f46e5; }
            </style>

            <div id="notification" style="position: fixed; top: 20px; right: -400px; background: white; padding: 20px 30px; border-radius: 20px; box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 15px; transition: all 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.68, -0.55, 0.265, 1.55); z-index: 9999; border-left: 5px solid var(--primary-purple);">
                <div style="width: 40px; height: 40px; background: var(--light-purple); border-radius: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: var(--primary-purple);">
                    <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <div style="font-weight: 800; color: var(--text-dark); font-size: 16px;">Заявка отправлена!</div>
                    <div style="color: #64748b; font-size: 14px;">Мы свяжемся с вами в ближайшее время.</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <script>
                document.getElementById('organizerRequestForm').addEventListener('submit', async (e) => {
                    e.preventDefault();
                    const form = e.target;
                    const formData = new FormData(form);
                    const data = Object.fromEntries(formData.entries());

                    try {
                        const response = await fetch('/contact/send', {
                            method: 'POST',
                            headers: {
                                'Content-Type': 'application/json'
                            },
                            body: JSON.stringify(data)
                        });

                        if (response.ok) {
                            const notification = document.getElementById('notification');
                            notification.style.right = '20px';
                            form.reset();
                            setTimeout(() => {
                                notification.style.right = '-400px';
                            }, 5000);
                        }
                    } catch (error) {
                        console.error('Error:', error);
                    }
                });
            </script>

            <div class="alt-cta" style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 30px; margin-bottom: 120px;">
                <div class="cta-card" style="background: #1e293b; color: #fff; padding: 60px; border-radius: 60px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: space-between; min-height: 500px; transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.2, 1, 0.3, 1); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05); position: relative; overflow: hidden;">
                    <div>
                        <h3 style="font-size: 3.2rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 25px; font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif; line-height: 1.1; margin-top: 0;">Станьте нашим <br><span style="font-family: 'Bellota', cursive; position: relative; display: inline-block;">партнёром<svg style="position: absolute; bottom: -8px; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 12px;" viewBox="0 0 100 12" preserveAspectRatio="none"><path d="M0,10 Q50,0 100,10" stroke="var(--primary-purple)" stroke-width="6" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></span></h3>
                        <p style="font-size: 18px; opacity: 0.7; margin-bottom: 40px; font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 400px;">Если у&nbsp;вас есть кафе, студия, лофт или база отдыха — и&nbsp;вы хотите принимать мероприятия&nbsp;и новых гостей, вам сюда.</p>
                    </div>
                    <a href="/partners" style="text-align: center; text-decoration: none; padding: 22px; border-radius: 24px; font-weight: 800; background: #e0e7ff; color: #4f46e5; font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; transition: all 0.3s ease; position: relative; z-index: 2;">Стать партнёром</a>
                </div>
                <div class="cta-card" style="background: var(--primary-purple); color: #fff; padding: 60px; border-radius: 60px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: space-between; min-height: 500px; transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.2, 1, 0.3, 1); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); position: relative; overflow: hidden;">
                    <div>
                        <h3 style="font-size: 3.2rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 25px; font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif; line-height: 1.1; margin-top: 0;">Стать <br><span style="font-family: 'Bellota', cursive; position: relative; display: inline-block;">организатором<svg style="position: absolute; bottom: -8px; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 12px;" viewBox="0 0 100 12" preserveAspectRatio="none"><path d="M0,10 Q50,0 100,10" stroke="white" stroke-width="6" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></span></h3>
                        <p style="font-size: 18px; opacity: 0.9; margin-bottom: 40px; font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 400px;">Хотите проводить мероприятия&nbsp;и находить благодарную аудиторию? Мы&nbsp;поможем вам вырасти.</p>
                    </div>
                    <a href="/auth/register" style="text-align: center; text-decoration: none; padding: 22px; border-radius: 24px; font-weight: 800; background: #1e293b; color: #fff; font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; transition: all 0.3s ease; position: relative; z-index: 2;">Начать сейчас</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <style>
                .cta-card:hover { transform: translateY(-10px) scale(1.01); box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.15); }
                .cta-card a:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); opacity: 0.9; }
            </style>
        </div>
    </main>

    <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
